description:
Fabiola Garcia specializes in individual, family, and couple's counseling working with issues such as transition in relationships (separation, infidelity, newly single, divorce), self-esteem, stress management, depression, anxiety, and sexual trauma.

Working with your anxiety, depression, and transitions. I will be there supporting you in a matter that you can continue your growth.
name: FABIOLA GARCIA, LMFT, NCC, QUALIFIED SUPERVISOR
